# 11. Music Transitions

Music changes smoothly during:

* Battle Start
* Battle End
* Velir Aram Entry
* Victory
* Main Menu

Transitions should use crossfading rather than abrupt stops.

---

# 12. Runtime Audio State

AudioManager tracks:

* Current Track
* Current Ambient Layer
* Active SFX
* Audio Bus Levels
* Transition State

Only one background track plays at any time.

---

# 13. Audio Resources

## MusicData

Stores:

* Track Name
* Audio File
* Loop Point
* Volume
* Category

---

## SoundEffectData

Stores:

* Effect Name
* Audio File
* Pitch Range
* Volume
* Category

---

## AmbientData

Stores:

* Ambient Name
* Loop
* Volume
* Environment

All audio assets should be loaded through Resources.

---

# 14. Audio Mixing

Recommended default mix:

| Bus     | Volume |
| ------- | ------ |
| Master  | 100%   |
| Music   | 70%    |
| Ambient | 50%    |
| SFX     | 90%    |
| UI      | 80%    |

Players can adjust every bus independently.

---

# 15. Signals

AudioManager exposes:

* music_started
* music_changed
* sfx_played
* ambience_changed
* audio_muted

Gameplay systems should trigger sounds through signals.

---

# 16. Performance Requirements

Audio Latency

< 50 ms

Music Transition

< 500 ms

Maximum Simultaneous SFX

16

Target Frame Rate

60 FPS

Audio should never affect gameplay performance.

---

